  42
  Schiller
  \&.\&.\&.\&.8<\-\-\-\- (no linefeed at the end)

bar\&.txt:
  \&.\&.\&.\&.8<\-\-\-\-
  lalala|*tanteratei
  \&.\&.\&.\&.8<\-\-\-\- (no linefeed at the end)

blob\&.txt
