\fIdependency\fR
to determine if the dependency has changed\&.
.RE
.sp
The
\fIfunction\fR
should return a
True
(non\-zero) value if the
\fIdependency\fR
has "changed" since the last time the
\fItarget\fR
was built (indicating that the target
\fIshould\fR
be rebuilt), and
