CheckContext\&.TryLink(\fIself\fR, \fItext\fR, \fIextension\fR)
.RS 4
Checks, if a file with the specified
\fIextension\fR
(e\&.g\&. \*(Aq\&.c\*(Aq) containing
\fItext\fR
can be compiled using the environment\*(Aqs
\fBProgram\fR
builder\&. Returns 1 on success and 0 on failure\&.
.RE
